<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Custom Deal Limit Assignment</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f5f7fa; 
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 20px auto; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .header h1 { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 28px; 
            font-weight: 300; 
        }
        .deal-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content { 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
        }
        .greeting { 
            font-size: 18px; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            color: #2c3e50; 
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .deal-limit {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .limit-label {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .assignment-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .detail-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
            gap: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #212529;
        }
        .increase {
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .decrease {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .same {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .benefits-section {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .benefits-section h4 {
            color: #155724;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        }
        .benefits-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .benefits-list li {
            padding: 8px 0 8px 30px;
            position: relative;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .benefits-list li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .usage-stats {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .usage-stats h4 {
            color: #856404;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-item {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .message-box h4 {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }
        .footer { 
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            padding: 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef; 
            color: #6c757d; 
        }
        .footer a { 
            color: #28a745; 
            text-decoration: none; 
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { margin: 10px; }
            .header, .content, .footer { padding: 20px; }
            .detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5px; }
            .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .btn { display: block; margin: 10px 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="deal-icon">ðŸŽ¯</div>
            <h1>Custom Deal Limit Assignment</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{merchantName}},
            </div>

            <p>Great news! Your deal posting limit has been updated by our admin team.</p>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="limit-label">Your New Monthly Deal Limit</div>
                <div class="deal-limit">{{newDealLimit}}</div>
                <div class="limit-label">Deals Per Month</div>
            </div>

            <div class="assignment-details">
                <h4>ðŸ“‹ Assignment Details</h4>
                <div class="detail-grid">
                    <span class="detail-label">Previous Limit:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{previousLimit}} deals/month</span>
                    
                    <span class="detail-label">New Limit:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{newDealLimit}} deals/month</span>
                    
                    <span class="detail-label">Change:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value {{changeClass}}">
                        {{#if isIncrease}}+{{/if}}{{change}} deals/month 
                        {{#if isIncrease}}(Increase){{else if isDecrease}}(Decrease){{else}}(No change){{/if}}
                    </span>
                    
                    <span class="detail-label">Effective Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{effectiveDate}}</span>
                    
                    <span class="detail-label">Assigned By:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{assignedBy}}</span>
                    
                    {{#if validUntil}}
                    <span class="detail-label">Valid Until:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{validUntil}}</span>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if adminMessage}}
            <div class="message-box">
                <h4>ðŸ’¬ Message from Admin</h4>
                <p>{{adminMessage}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if isIncrease}}
            <div class="benefits-section">
                <h4>ðŸš€ What this means for you:</h4>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                    <li>Post more deals to reach more customers</li>
                    <li>Increase your business visibility</li>
                    <li>Boost sales with additional promotional opportunities</li>
                    <li>Better compete in your category</li>
                    {{#if isPremiumLimit}}
                    <li>Access to premium merchant features</li>
                    <li>Priority listing in deal categories</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="usage-stats">
                <h4>ðŸ“Š Current Month Usage</h4>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{dealsUsedThisMonth}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Deals Posted</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{remainingDeals}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Remaining</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{totalRedemptions}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Total Redemptions</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">{{activeDeals}}</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Active Deals</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{createDealUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">Create New Deal</a>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">View Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            {{#if tips}}
            <div class="benefits-section">
                <h4>ðŸ’¡ Tips to Maximize Your Deal Limit:</h4>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                    <li>Create deals with clear, attractive descriptions</li>
                    <li>Use high-quality images to showcase your offers</li>
                    <li>Set competitive pricing to attract more customers</li>
                    <li>Monitor deal performance and adjust as needed</li>
                    <li>Respond quickly to customer redemption requests</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p>This change takes effect immediately. You can start posting deals up to your new limit right away.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions about your new deal limit or need assistance with posting deals, our support team is here to help.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for being a valued merchant partner!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The Platform Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>Visit your <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}">Merchant Dashboard</a> | <a href="{{helpUrl}}">Help Center</a></p>
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: {{supportEmail}} | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>
